Dialogue: 1,0:44:54.53,0:44:56.37,ED song english,,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur1.5\fad(200,200)\org(0,0)}Chìm trong quên lãng
Dialogue: 1,0:44:56.19,0:44:58.31,ED song english,,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur1.5\fad(200,200)\org(0,0)}Trong đêm thâu
Dialogue: 1,0:44:58.13,0:45:02.84,ED song english,,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur1.5\fad(200,200)\org(0,0)}Ta mơ về một bóng râm buổi trưa
